{
  "texts": [
    "Each initial item will be assigned a survey option ranging from 1 to 7 points, with 1 indicating strong disagreement and 7 indicating strong agreement.",
    "All statistics will be based on median scores.",
    "If the median score is between 1 and 3, the items will be excluded.",
    "If the score is 4 or 5 (or higher with substantial comments on the content), the item will be discussed and entered into the next round of the Delphi survey or the consensus meeting.",
    "If the score is 6 or 7 without any substantial comments, the item will be included in the final checklist."
  ]
}